if\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好多牆被清 噴字被油<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁咪搵過第二個地點/時間<br />\n守24小時呀笨"},{"pid":"0109211e51d8693af054a6b72c972facc7394574","tid":1674841,"uid":31925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T12:50:12.000Z","msg":"標題要改善"},{"pid":"b5fc7a395deed16e41dc2d21a5c5c12284c35cc2","tid":1674841,"uid":256505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T12:53:54.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">撕左咪再貼，有輸嬴嫁咩</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f43355f4716203b78710fc9b4e2286217fe55bbd","tid":1674841,"uid":28831,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T12:54:35.000Z","msg":"流動連儂牆囉<br />\n行到邊貼到邊<br />\n唔洗死守一個地方<br />\n睇佢點清睇佢點巡<br />\n<br />\n落返地行咇囉唔驚比人扔汽油彈既話"},{"pid":"4d2d8bfb5310a9c2dbd531581795cd2a8354f044","tid":1674841,"uid":61786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e6e88aab2de2b024851b065bf7fb925071f96c11","tid":1674841,"uid":53612,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T12:45:00.000Z","msg":"補牆小心，不定時 快<br />\n警伏人亂拉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T12:56:22.000Z","msg":"啱啱葵涌村拉左喇！屌！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"230f3af39d6e72e92724eafb7bad18583e901cac","tid":1674841,"uid":148253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T12:56:41.000Z","msg":"屌你，咪撚成日用埋呢d字眼，應該講打壓連儂牆香港人唔會怕，繼續撕一貼百!!!"},{"pid":"4e0c48e80fae21c1396ee8b82a73fd22a2291c1c","tid":1674841,"uid":154702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T12:56:45.000Z","msg":"捉撚到咩<br />\n食環放人守地<br />\n守得幾多？ <br />\n<br />\n袋住隨街貼<br />\n貼果下先犯法<br />\n袋就無事<br />\n搵人跟足我一日丫笨"},{"pid":"8d65db9f1a35e096f919506ac4deea9a4afa6383","tid":1674841,"uid":53612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e0c48e80fae21c1396ee8b82a73fd22a2291c1c","tid":1674841,"uid":154702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T12:56:45.000Z","msg":"捉撚到咩<br />\n食環放人守地<br />\n守得幾多？ <br />\n<br />\n袋住隨街貼<br />\n貼果下先犯法<br />\n袋就無事<br />\n搵人跟足我一日丫笨"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T12:59:34.000Z","msg":"大家改下策略，袋住貼<br />\n唔定時，唔定地方"},{"pid":"636bbefa5b741d8410a98466b939faf5c6846f9a","tid":1674841,"uid":42304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T13:05:37.000Z","msg":"只要人多，5分鐘可以完事散水"},{"pid":"46a5588b42f16e8e614ea6b2f18901b0153f0b3d","tid":1674841,"uid":286309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T13:09:14.000Z","msg":"牆可以再起過 成本：紙<br />\n強行守護牆 成本：文宣手足被打＋popo亂尻拉人<br />\n<br />\n牆嘅意義係要有資訊俾到路人<br />\n並非無損壞咁淨係存在"},{"pid":"fbc58496fa510904f02f4365bd9c9db8fca80225","tid":1674841,"uid":263230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T18:26:03.000Z","msg":"都係果句，人多就最安全"}]}